summary: An ordinance relating to the Engineering Dept., authorizing preparation of plans and specifications for a limited access arterial highway improvement on S.W. Spokane Street from Iowa Ave. Southwest to 36th Ave. S.W. in the vicinity of Avalon Way Southwest; authorizing construction of a portion of said improvement, making a partially reimbursable appropriation from the Seattle General Street Improvements Bonds 1960 Fund therefor, and superseding Ordinance 88583.
